		{
			"name": "获取 Access Token",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.status === \"OK\") {",
							"  const data = pm.response.json();",
							"  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', data.accessToken);",
							"  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', data.refreshToken);",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"su\",\n  \"password\": \"111\"\n}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{host}}/api/v1/token",
					"host": [
						"{{host}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"v1",
						"token"
					]
				},
				"description": "## 请求参数\n\nJSON 请求体：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"username\": \"...\", // 用户名，必填，长度 <= 100\n  \"password\": \"...\" // 密码，必填，长度 <= 100\n}\n```\n\n## 返回值\n\n成功时：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"accessToken\": \"...\", // 要获取的 Access Token\n  \"refreshToken\": \"...\", // 用于刷新的 Refresh Token\n  \"expiresIn\": 1800, // Access Token 的有效期（秒为单位，有效期 30 分钟）\n  \"username\": \"zhangsan\", // 用户名\n  \"nickname\": \"张三\", // 昵称\n  \"authorities\": [\"user\"] // 权限列表\n}\n```\n\n失败时：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"2022-09-15 10:25:13\",\n  \"status\": 500,\n  \"error\": \"Internal Server Error\", // 错误信息\n  \"path\": \"/api/v1/token\"\n}\n```"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "刷新 Access Token",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.status === \"OK\") {",
							"  const data = pm.response.json();",
							"  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', data.accessToken);",
							"  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', data.refreshToken);",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Authorization",
						"value": "123",
						"type": "text"
					},
					{
						"key": "Accept",
						"value": "text/html",
						"type": "text",
						"disabled": true
					}
				],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{host}}/api/v1/token/{{refreshToken}}",
					"host": [
						"{{host}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"v1",
						"token",
						"{{refreshToken}}"
					]
				},
				"description": "## 请求参数\n\nURL 路径参数：\n\n```url\n/api/v1/token/{refreshToken}\n```\n\n## 返回值\n\n成功时：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"accessToken\": \"...\", // 要获取的 Access Token\n  \"refreshToken\": \"...\", // 用于刷新的 Refresh Token\n  \"expiresIn\": 1800, // Access Token 的有效期（秒为单位，有效期 30 分钟）\n  \"username\": \"zhangsan\", // 用户名\n  \"nickname\": \"张三\", // 昵称\n  \"authorities\": [\"user\"] // 权限列表\n}\n```\n\n失败时：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"2022-09-15 10:25:13\",\n  \"status\": 500,\n  \"error\": \"Internal Server Error\", // 错误信息\n  \"path\": \"/api/v1/token\"\n}\n```"
			},
			"response": []
		}
